---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About | Rao Xu" description="About Rao Xu, SAP Basis consultant.">
  <main class="container hero prose">
    <h1 class="page-title">About Rao Xu / 关于我</h1>
    <p>I work in SAP Basis and focus on stable SAP operations, maintainable landscapes and long-term technical reliability. This site presents my professional profile and technical writing in bilingual form.</p>
    <p>我从事 SAP Basis，关注 SAP 系统的稳定运行、可维护架构与长期技术可靠性。这个网站以中英文双语形式呈现我的专业方向与技术写作。</p>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="card"><h3>Focus / 关注点</h3><p>SAP landscape administration, monitoring, migration, backup and recovery.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Style / 风格</h3><p>Calm, direct, structured, and execution-first.</p></article>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
